column1: With the Supreme Court getting ready to hear arguments in a case that could result in Roe v. Wade being struck down the time to act is now.
Healthcare choices should be between patients and their doctor. Politicians have no place in that decision-making process. https://t.co/Is3YPbjQ7E

Keeping Americans safe and secure are my greatest responsibilities as your representative in Congress. I will continue to put the interests of our nation and people first not politics. https://t.co/cNBZfVaMmR
Merry Christmas from my family to yours. May the spirit of the holidays bring you joy and happiness! https://t.co/cPU5lmyljD
